Simple Analogy

Think of a vector database as a smart librarian.

Books = Your PDFs or documents
Book summaries = Embeddings
Librarian = Vector database
Reader = User
Answer writer = LLM (ChatGPT/Gemini)

When you ask a question:

The librarian (vector database) quickly finds the most relevant books.
The writer (LLM) reads those books and explains the answer in simple language.

